{"tid":362472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這些尊貴的香港議員聲稱香港有法治，你叫外國點幫你？","createTime":"2017-08-17T03:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T03:30:48.000Z","uid":53379,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a820c8bfe1fd18eb905876c572328bce00b54472","tid":362472,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"英國國會議員在71 時曾為抗爭者受審及議員被DQ ，求問英國外交部關注。外交部卻答覆香港有良好法治及司法獨立。正正就是這些尊貴的香港議員聲稱香港有法治，你叫外國點幫你？<br />\n<br />\n現正呼籲法律界朋友聯絡我地，submit Written Evidence！清楚解釋現在香港法治的情況！多謝！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/1794708487213977:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCPForum%2Fposts%2F1794708487213977%3A0&d=UlEy9l6EmTdir9krYDVFQU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=fd02b02a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/1794708487213977:0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20799188_1830798890271603_8000147308589737653_n.jpg?oh=5bfecb36a585d53eff10d8e24ba132d6&amp;oe=5A389917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20799188_1830798890271603_8000147308589737653_n.jpg%3Foh%3D5bfecb36a585d53eff10d8e24ba132d6%26oe%3D5A389917&h=cc0f7670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/l/t1.0-9/20915338_1830798893604936_8032057650302416631_n.jpg?oh=8175398cea0a9c7a0ee37bf3d5a2d16e&amp;oe=5A233C10\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Fl%2Ft1.0-9%2F20915338_1830798893604936_8032057650302416631_n.jpg%3Foh%3D8175398cea0a9c7a0ee37bf3d5a2d16e%26oe%3D5A233C10&h=d3435ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20840962_1830798896938269_9040947739542913645_n.jpg?oh=08822a66e67c8db8cd66984b01d978cd&amp;oe=5A2A8E5E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0